@startuml sequence_admin
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #333
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #555
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #AAA
autonumber

title Sequence 3 — Admin: Login & Component Management

actor "Admin" as A
participant "Admin Panel\n(React)" as ADM
participant "POST /api/auth/login" as LOGIN
participant "Admin Routes\n(JWT-protected)" as API
participant "ComponentService" as SVC
database "PostgreSQL" as DB

== Login ==

A -> ADM : Enter username + password
ADM -> LOGIN : POST /api/auth/login\n{ username, password }
LOGIN -> DB : SELECT admins WHERE username = ?
DB --> LOGIN : admin row (password_hash)
LOGIN -> LOGIN : bcrypt.compare(password, hash)

alt invalid credentials
  LOGIN --> ADM : 401 Unauthorized
  ADM --> A : "Invalid credentials"
else valid
  LOGIN -> DB : INSERT refresh_tokens (hash, expires 7d)
  LOGIN --> ADM : 200 { access_token (15min JWT) }\n+ Set-Cookie: refresh_token (HttpOnly, 7d)
  ADM --> A : Redirect to Dashboard
end

== Create a Component ==

A -> ADM : Fill component form\n(category: cpu, socket: AM5, ...)
ADM -> API : POST /api/admin/components\nAuthorization: Bearer <token>\nbody: { category, name, socket, ... }
API -> API : authMiddleware — verify JWT
API -> API : validateComponent — Zod schema\nfor the given category
API -> SVC : createComponent(data)
SVC -> DB : INSERT INTO components\nRETURNING *
DB --> SVC : new component row
SVC -> DB : INSERT admin_activity_log\n(action: component_created)
SVC --> API : component object
API --> ADM : 201 Created — component
ADM --> A : Component appears in list

== Link an Unmatched Listing ==

A -> ADM : Open Unmatched Listings page
ADM -> API : GET /api/admin/unmatched-listings?status=pending
API --> ADM : { listings: [...] }
A -> ADM : Click "Link" on a listing\nSearch and select a component
ADM -> API : POST /api/admin/unmatched-listings/:id/link\n{ component_id: 42 }
API -> DB : INSERT scraper_mappings\n(component_id, retailer_id, product_url)\nON CONFLICT DO UPDATE
API -> DB : UPDATE unmatched_listings\nSET status = 'linked'
API --> ADM : 200 { success: true }
ADM --> A : Listing marked as linked\n(next scrape will price it correctly)

@enduml
